型冠狀病毒，住進巴勒斯坦的希布倫省立醫院（Hebron State Hospital）加護病房接受5天治療。有媒體提到，這間病房位於2樓。"},{"pid":"b4151deef4552ae59dd3bafeb3bc86f39a2d5d32","tid":2119002,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:48:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52e5d680d4029e0704e05db038eb5d5336ffd693","tid":2119002,"uid":121989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"坐喺抽氣扇出風口位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd10a8e520b1f4b65fbe4d963ceadff377010fc","tid":2119002,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T01:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nw9dfer.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNw9dfer.gif&h=3c3c2223&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fg5Px07.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffg5Px07.gif&h=8b60eee3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a040dc5905c27647ca8a6234be798a0eecdea462","tid":2119002,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4151deef4552ae59dd3bafeb3bc86f39a2d5d32","tid":2119002,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:48:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T01:11:27.000Z","msg":"會員 #252142 - HKUSecret 極有可能係五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍<br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n該會員以往言論 (7)：<br />\n1 .lih.kg/fxMAvT藍屍言論<br />\n2 .lih.kg/fuEkpT藍屍言論<br />\n3 .lih.kg/fuqPkT藍屍言論<br />\n4 .lih.kg/ftmMQT假消息標題黨<br />\n5 .lih.kg/fsyJPT藍屍言論<br />\n6 .lih.kg/frMmBT藍屍言論<br />\n7 .lih.kg/fijEyT藍屍言論"}]}